uot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Verdana, \'Lucida Grande\', Lucida, sans-serif; line-height: 15px; text-align: left; &quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_word&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; &quot;&gt;Flavor&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_explanation&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; &quot;&gt;Smaak. Elektronische sigaretten zijn in diverse smaken te verkrijgen. De smaak wordt bepaald door het soort smaakstof dat in de e-vloeistof werd toegevoegd.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Verdana, \'Lucida Grande\', Lucida, sans-serif; line-height: 15px; text-align: left; &quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_word&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; &quot;&gt;Flooding&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_explanation&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; &quot;&gt;Dit gebeurt wanneer er teveel e-vloeistof in de atomizer zit.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Verdana, \'Lucida Grande\', Lucida, sans-serif; line-height: 15px; text-align: left; &quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_word&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; &quot;&gt;LED&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_explanation&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; &quot;&gt;Light Emitting Diode. Dit is het lampje dat aangeeft wanneer de batterij geactiveerd is. Bovendien wordt deze LED als indicator gebruikt bij het laden van de batterij.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Verdana, \'Lucida Grande\', Lucida, sans-serif; line-height: 15px; text-align: left; &quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_word&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; &quot;&gt;LR-atomizer&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_explanation&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; &quot;&gt;LR staat voor Lage Resolutie. Een LR-atomizer kan de vloeistof meer verhitten, waardoor meer damp wordt gegenereerd.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Verdana, \'Lucida Grande\', Lucida, sans-serif; line-height: 15px; text-align: left; &quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_word&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; &quot;&gt;Manuele batterij / Manuele sigaret&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_explanation&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; &quot;&gt;In tegenstelling tot een automatische batterij is dit en batterij met drukknopje. Met dit drukknopje bepaalt de gebruiker manueel wanneer hij de atomizer onder stroom zet. Dit laat toe om bijvoorbeeld voor te gloeien. Het systeem heeft zijn voor-en nadelen.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Verdana, \'Lucida Grande\', Lucida, sans-serif; line-height: 15px; text-align: left; &quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_word&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; &quot;&gt;Mini-Sigaret&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_explanation&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; &quot;&gt;Een elektronische sigaret die kleiner is dan een gemiddelde sigaret, vaak is een mini-sigaret ongeveer even groot als een analoge sigaret.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Verdana, \'Lucida Grande\', Lucida, sans-serif; line-height: 15px; text-align: left; &quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_word&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; &quot;&gt;MOD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_explanation&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; &quot;&gt;Een MOD of modificatie is een aanpassing van Ã©Ã©n van de componenten met als doel ze beter te laten presteren. Meestal is het de bedoeling om meer rook te genereren of betere batterijprestaties te bekomen. Dit is niet ongevaarlijk en heeft wel eens een ongewenste explosie tot gevolg gehad.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Verdana, \'Lucida Grande\', Lucida, sans-serif; line-height: 15px; text-align: left; &quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_word&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; &quot;&gt;Mondstukje / Mouthpiece&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_explanation&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; &quot;&gt;Het stukje dat de e-roker in de mond neemt, bij de analoge sigaret een filter.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Verdana, \'Lucida Grande\', Lucida, sans-serif; line-height: 15px; text-align: left; &quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_word&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; &quot;&gt;Nicotine Level&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_explanation&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; &quot;&gt;De hoeveelheid nicotine aanwezig in de cartridge of e-vloeistof. Meestal uitgedrukt in mg/ml of %&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Verdana, \'Lucida Grande\', Lucida, sans-serif; line-height: 15px; text-align: left; &quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_word&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; &quot;&gt;Pass-through batterij (PT)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_explanation&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; &quot;&gt;Een elektronische sigaret voorzien van een kabeltje met USB connector. Deze sigaret werkt op de stroom die via de USB poort wordt aangeleverd. Losgekoppeld kan ze niet gebruikt worden. Voornamelijk ideaal voor kantoorwerk of in de wagen.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Verdana, \'Lucida Grande\', Lucida, sans-serif; line-height: 15px; text-align: left; &quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_word&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; &quot;&gt;Pen-Style / Penstijl&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_explanation&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; &quot;&gt;Een bepaald type elektronische sigaret dat qua uiterlijk lijkt op een pen.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Verdana, \'Lucida Grande\', Lucida, sans-serif; line-height: 15px; text-align: left; &quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_word&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; &quot;&gt;Personal Vaporizer (PV) / Persoonlijke Nicotine Dispenser (PND)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_explanation&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; &quot;&gt;Een andere benaming voor een elektronische sigaret.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Verdana, \'Lucida Grande\', Lucida, sans-serif; line-height: 15px; text-align: left; &quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_word&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; &quot;&gt;Plantaardige Glycerine (VG)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_explanation&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; &quot;&gt;Plantaardige Glycerine of Vegetable Glycerin is een drager van e-vloeistof. Het is een alternatief voor Propyleen Glycol (PG). Het wordt soms gebruikt omdat mensen allergisch zijn voor PG. Het gebruik is echter aan een aantal voorwaarden gebonden. Zo is het niet aan te raden VG te gebruiken in combinatie met LR-atomizers daar de verhitting zo extreem is dat er kankerverwekkende stoffen vrijkomen.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Verdana, \'Lucida Grande\', Lucida, sans-serif; line-height: 15px; text-align: left; &quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_word&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; &quot;&gt;Polyfill&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_explanation&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; &quot;&gt;Het wattenmateriaal dat zich in een cartomizer bevindt om de e-vloeistof vast te houden.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Verdana, \'Lucida Grande\', Lucida, sans-serif; line-height: 15px; text-align: left; &quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_word&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; &quot;&gt;Propyleen Glycol (PG)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_explanation&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; &quot;&gt;Propyleen Glycol is een stof die als drager of basis gebruikt wordt van de e-vloeistof.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Verdana, \'Lucida Grande\', Lucida, sans-serif; line-height: 15px; text-align: left; &quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_word&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; &quot;&gt;Refilling&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_explanation&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; &quot;&gt;Het vullen van een lege cartridge met nieuwe e-vloeistof&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Verdana, \'Lucida Grande\', Lucida, sans-serif; line-height: 15px; text-align: left; &quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_word&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; &quot;&gt;Starter Kit&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_explanation&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; &quot;&gt;Een complete kit die alles bevat wat je nodig hebt om elektronisch te kunnen roken. In principe bevat de kit Ã©Ã©n of meerdere batterijen, atomizers en cartridges of cartomizers, een lader en een handleiding.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Verdana, \'Lucida Grande\', Lucida, sans-serif; line-height: 15px; text-align: left; &quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_word&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; &quot;&gt;Tank / (liquid)-tank&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_explanation&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; &quot;&gt;Bepaalde types elektronische sigaretten maken in tegenstelling tot een cartridge of cartomizer gebruik van een klein tankje waarin de vloeistof wordt opgeslagen.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Verdana, \'Lucida Grande\', Lucida, sans-serif; line-height: 15px; text-align: left; &quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_word&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; &quot;&gt;Throat-hit&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_explanation&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; &quot;&gt;De rook die je inhaleert genereert een bepaald gevoel achteraan in de keel en/of longen van de roker. Throat-hit is de Engelse term die wordt gebruikt om deze sensatie weer te geven. Het roken van een analoge (traditionele) sigaret zorgt voor een kriebel in de keel. Throat-hit geeft aan hoe nauw het gevoel deze kriebel benadert. Naast het nicotine level zijn er tal van factoren die een rol hierin spelen. In het Nederlands wordt soms ook de term &quot;gier&quot; gebruikt.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Verdana, \'Lucida Grande\', Lucida, sans-serif; line-height: 15px; text-align: left; &quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_word&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; &quot;&gt;Topping off&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_explanation&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; &quot;&gt;Bijvullen of Topping off is het fenomeen van een paar druppels e-vloeistof toe te voegen aan een cartridge die bijna leeg is.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Verdana, \'Lucida Grande\', Lucida, sans-serif; line-height: 15px; text-align: left; &quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_word&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; &quot;&gt;Trekken / Trek&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_explanation&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; &quot;&gt;Aan het mondstuk zuigen om rook naar de mond of longen te laten circuleren.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_word&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; &quot;&gt;Tripple Coil&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_explanation&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; &quot;&gt;Een tripple coil cartomizer beschikt over drie gloeispiralen. Hierdoor is er een lagere weerstand en kan er meer rook geproduceerd worden. Het gebruik van dual coil cartomizers heeft een aantal consequenties wat betreft batterij en vloeistofkeuze.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Verdana, \'Lucida Grande\', Lucida, sans-serif; line-height: 15px; text-align: left; &quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_word&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; &quot;&gt;Vapen&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_explanation&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; &quot;&gt;Een gangbare benaming voor het roken van een elektronische sigaret.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Verdana, \'Lucida Grande\', Lucida, sans-serif; line-height: 15px; text-align: left; &quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_word&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; &quot;&gt;Vapor / Vapour&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;explanatory_dictionary_explanation&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; &quot;&gt;Vapor of damp is hetgeen geproduceerd wordt wanneer de e-vloeistof van vloeibaar naar gasvorm wordt omgezet. De damp die geproduceerd wordt is een soort geurloze waterdamp die onschadelijk en geurloos is.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Verdana, \'Lucida Grande\', Lucida, sans-serif; line-height: 15px; text-align: left; &quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; &quot;&gt;\r\n		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','',''),(91,1,'Lexicon','','',''),(79,1,'Refillables','','',''),(59,2,'Batterijen','&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://www.startvaping.nl/image/data/batterijen/titans.jpg&quot; style=&quot;width: 669px; height: 136px; &quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','',''),(59,1,'Batterij','&lt;p&gt;\r\n	batterij eng cat&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','',''),(84,2,'Elektronisch Roken','&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h4 style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-family: Helvetica; min-height: 14px; &quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; &quot;&gt;Over E-Sigaretten&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 18px; font-family: Helvetica; &quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; &quot;&gt;Nog nooit was stoppen met roken makkelijker.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	Schakel probleemloos over van gewone sigaretten&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://www.startvaping.nl/image/data/Plaatjes/welcome.jpg&quot; style=&quot;float: right; width: 366px; height: 254px; &quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	naar elektronische sigaretten (e-sigaretten)&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	E-sigaretten zijn veel minder schadelijk en bovendien&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	een stuk goedkoper!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h4 style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 18px; font-family: Helvetica; &quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; &quot;&gt;Wat is nou precies een elektronische sigaret?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 18px; font-family: Helvetica; &quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; &quot;&gt;Elektronische sigarettenâook wel e-sigaretten of&amp;nbsp;e-sigs genoemd âzijn een uitstekend alternatief voor gewone&amp;nbsp;sigaretten. Elektronische sigaretten produceren een damp die&amp;nbsp;je uitblaast en dezelfde sensatie geeft als gewoon roken.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	En wat zo leuk is: je hebt wel 150 verschillende smaakjes&amp;nbsp;die je kunt verdampen. Zo wordt een sigaret nog lekkerder.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	En je rookt niet meer, je&amp;nbsp;dampt! (vapen in het Engels)&amp;nbsp;Dampen&amp;nbsp;voelt precies als gewoon roken maar dan wel zonder &amp;nbsp;de teer,&amp;nbsp;de schadelijke stoffen en de stank.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 18px; font-family: Helvetica; &quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; &quot;&gt;Het is meer een relaxmoment, alleen of met vrienden.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h4 style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 18px; font-family: Helvetica; &quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; &quot;&gt;Voordelen van E-sigaretten van Startvaping&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 18px; font-family: Helvetica; &quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; &quot;&gt;Als je eenmaal onze e-sigaretten geprobeerd hebt wil je niets anders meer.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 18px; font-family: Helvetica; &quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 148, 3); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h3 style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 24px; font-family: Helvetica; &quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://www.startvaping.nl/image/data/Plaatjes/value.jpg&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 148, 3); width: 56px; height: 56px; margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px; float: left; &quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#329403;&quot;&gt;Groot voordeel&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 24px 120px; font-family: Helvetica; &quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; &quot;&gt;E-sigaretten kosten binnen korte tijd veel minder dan traditionele sigaretten.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	Als je bijvoorbeeld 1 pakje per dag rookt dan ben je zo 46 euro per week kwijt.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	Bij Startvaping is een starterskit verkrijgbaar vanaf â¬ 39,95. Die heb je dus zo terug verdiend.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	Daarna heb je alleen nog maar vloeistoffen nodig en wat filters. Een flesje van 30 ml&amp;nbsp;kost bij&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	ons â¬ 12,50 en daar kan je makkeljk voor een maand sigaretten uit halen.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	Tel dus uit&amp;nbsp;je winst.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&lt;h3 style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 24px; font-family: Helvetica; &quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://www.startvaping.nl/image/data/Plaatjes/clean.jpg&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 148, 3); width: 56px; height: 56px; margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px; float: left; &quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 148, 3); &quot;&gt;Schoner dan gewone sigaretten&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 24px 120px; font-family: Helvetica; &quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; &quot;&gt;E-sigaretten geven geen rook omdat ze niets verbranden. Ze verdampen alleen maar en&lt;br /&gt;\r\n		damp&amp;nbsp;krijg je ook als je bijvoorbeeld thee zet.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; &quot; /&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; &quot;&gt;Je hebt geen vieze rooklucht meer in huis en ook niet meer in je haren en kleren.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; &quot; /&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; &quot;&gt;Geen teer, geen vieze volle asbakken meer.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; &quot; /&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; &quot;&gt;En daarnaast geen vlekken meer op je vingers of aanslag op je tanden.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&lt;h3 style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 24px; font-family: Helvetica; &quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://www.startvaping.nl/image/data/Plaatjes/steps.jpg&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 148, 3); width: 56px; height: 56px; margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px; float: left; &quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 148, 3); &quot;&gt;Goed gemaakt&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n		&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 24px 120px; font-family: Helvetica; &quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; &quot;&gt;Details zijn belangrijk. Onze lithium ion batterijen zijn uitgebreid getest op kwaliteit,&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			iets dat vaak door andere leveranciers wordt overgeslagen.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			Onze batterijen gaan lang(er) mee, zien er mooi&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; &quot;&gt;vormgegeven uit en onze vloeistoffen&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			zijn het beste van smaak.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			Bij ons krijgt u echt waar voor uw geld&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; &quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n		&lt;div&gt;\r\n			&lt;div&gt;\r\n				&lt;h3 style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 24px; font-family: Helvetica; &quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://www.startvaping.nl/image/data/Plaatjes/house.jpg&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 148, 3); width: 56px; height: 56px; margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px; float: left; &quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 148, 3); &quot;&gt;Mag overal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 24px 120px; font-family: Helvetica; &quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; &quot;&gt;Vapen is overal toegestaan. Waarom? Omdat je geen vervuilende stank achterlaat.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; &quot; /&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; &quot;&gt;Meestal kun je zonder problemen dampen/vapen in restaurants, cafe\'s, winkels en&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					andere plaatsen&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; &quot;&gt;waar roken verboden is.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; &quot; /&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; &quot;&gt;Je kunt nu probleemloos dampen/vapen in huis, in je auto of zelfs op je werk.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					Hoef je in de winter ook&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; &quot;&gt;niet meer buiten staan te verkleumen.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;div&gt;\r\n					&lt;div&gt;\r\n						&lt;h3 style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 24px; font-family: Helvetica; &quot;&gt;\r\n							&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://www.startvaping.nl/image/data/Plaatjes/happy.jpg&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 148, 3); width: 56px; height: 56px; margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px; float: left; &quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(50, 148, 3); &quot;&gt;Lekker&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n						&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 24px 120px; font-family: Helvetica; &quot;&gt;\r\n							&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; &quot;&gt;Dampen is net als roken, je kunt ringetjes blazen, je houdt het gevoel in je keel&lt;br /&gt;\r\n							(throat-hit of ook&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; &quot;&gt;wel gier genoemd) en zelfs de tabaksmaak kun je houden.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; &quot; /&gt;\r\n							&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; &quot;&gt;Daarnaast zijn er meer dan 150 verschillende smaken waaruit je kan kiezen zoals&lt;br /&gt;\r\n							bijvoorbeeld Koffie, Menthol, Frisdrank of een Fruit- of zoete snoep-smaak.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; &quot; /&gt;\r\n							&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; &quot;&gt;De vloeistoffen die wij leveren torenen hoog boven veel andere smaken uit.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n							Je merkt onmiddellijk&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; &quot;&gt;het verschil!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n					&lt;/div&gt;\r\n				&lt;/div&gt;\r\n			&lt;/div&gt;\r\n		&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;h4 style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 18px; font-family: Helvetica; &quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; &quot;&gt;Hoe werkt een e-sigaret?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 18px; font-family: Helvetica; &quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; &quot;&gt;De vloeistof die je in de e-sig doet gaat in een soort filter genoemd de Cartomizer.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	Deze cartomizers zijn leeg verkrijgbaar zodat je ze kunt navullen of je kunt ze&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	voorgevuld bestellen. Ook deze voorgevulde cartomizers zijn navulbaar (een keer of 6 of tot&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	de smaak niet meer lekker is)&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	De cartomozer schroef je vast aan de batterij die de vloeistof verhit zodra je een trekje neemt&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	waardoor er dus damp ontstaat die je kunt inhaleren en weer uitblazen.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://www.startvaping.nl/image/data/Plaatjes/e-cigarette.jpg&quot; style=&quot;width: 460px; height: 173px; &quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','',''),(86,1,'Refillables','','',''),(92,2,'Probeerset','','e liquid probeerset','e-liquid, e-liquids, smaken, flavor, nicotine sterkte, nicotine level, fruit, tabak, mentol, juice, pg, vg, propyleen glycol, vegetable glycrine, plantaardige glycerine, elektrisch roken, elektronisch roken,  e-sigaret, e- sigaretten, e-sig, e-cig, e-ciga'),(92,1,'Probeerset','','',''),(93,2,'Probeersets','','',''),(93,1,'Probeerset','','','');
